reviewText: why can't this be bought on DVD ?
this is classic. I cannot believe it is not somehow available

If you are reading this review then you know how rare this special from Ann is.  An absolute must for all fans.  This film is how I learned about Ann for the first time.  Made for TV has me in stitches every time.  If Ann makes you laugh, then this is for you.  This is your chance to see Vulcan Death Grip!
